trans-unit.source: Base class for all the chart elements.
trans-unit.target: Basklass för alla element i organisationsschemat.

trans-unit.source: The ChartElement class represents the most basic element of the chart element hierarchy.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ChartElement representerar det mest grundläggande elementet i diagrammet elementet hierarkin.
